Interface Converter<F,T>

  • Type Parameters:
    F - The type being converted from.
    T - The type being converted to.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Converter.IdentityConverter, JsonValueToJsonBytesConverter, LongToCalendarConverter, MapToJsonBytesConverter, MapToJsonStringConverter, RequestingPartyToken.PermissionsSetConverter, SetToJsonBytesConverter

    public interface Converter<F,T>
    A custom converter that allows non-CTS-native types to be converted to those that can be stored.
